        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Pretrial Integrity and Safety Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of Justice Programs within the Department of Justice to make grants (1) to replace bail systems that use payment of money as a condition of pretrial release in criminal cases, and (2) to implement a National Pretrial Reporting Program to collect data on the processing of defendants by state and local courts.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
